574
00:19:11,960 --> 00:19:13,019
We're both fathers, right?

575
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:14,359
Right?

576
00:19:14,900 --> 00:19:16,420
We can't just let

577
00:19:16,420 --> 00:19:18,059
the kids run wild on their whims.

578
00:19:18,619 --> 00:19:18,900
Here's the thing.

579
00:19:19,019 --> 00:19:20,160
Let's you and me first

580
00:19:20,339 --> 00:19:21,200
hash this whole thing out.

581
00:19:22,019 --> 00:19:23,240
In the end, the kids' marriage

582
00:19:23,579 --> 00:19:24,839
is up to us two dads, isn't it?

583
00:19:25,160 --> 00:19:25,579
Am I right?

584
00:19:27,200 --> 00:19:28,420
How did your son end up

585
00:19:28,420 --> 00:19:29,759
with a father like you?

586
00:19:29,960 --> 00:19:31,220
He's really out of luck.

587
00:19:32,220 --> 00:19:33,980
Cursed for eight generations.

588
00:19:34,680 --> 00:19:35,539
Xiaofang's affairs

589
00:19:37,480 --> 00:19:38,180
are hers to decide.

590
00:19:45,980 --> 00:19:47,059
You're the useless one,

591
00:19:47,079 --> 00:19:48,079
and yet you act righteous?

592
00:19:48,400 --> 00:19:49,980
No wonder your wife ran off with someone.

593
00:19:50,279 --> 00:19:51,759
Back then you couldn't control your wife,

594
00:19:52,279 --> 00:19:53,900
now you can't control your daughter.

595
00:19:59,039 --> 00:19:59,779
Yang Fanhu!

596
00:19:59,880 --> 00:20:01,059
Who are you calling a dog?

597
00:20:01,619 --> 00:20:03,819
Just you wait, you'll get yours.

598
00:20:06,019 --> 00:20:07,819
I could just bite you to death!

599
00:20:12,559 --> 00:20:13,440
I'm so mad!

600
00:20:17,200 --> 00:20:17,759
Huzi.

601
00:20:23,220 --> 00:20:23,740
I steamed these.

602
00:20:24,819 --> 00:20:25,400
Fresh out of the pot.

603
00:20:26,480 --> 00:20:27,000
These are for you.

604
00:20:32,720 --> 00:20:36,059
Two little tigers, two little tigers,

605
00:20:36,319 --> 00:20:37,079
running so...

606
00:20:39,859 --> 00:20:40,440
Okay, okay, here.

607
00:20:41,539 --> 00:20:42,500
Do you still remember?

608
00:20:42,900 --> 00:20:43,940
Back then you loved eating

609
00:20:43,940 --> 00:20:45,059
the buns I steamed.

610
00:20:45,420 --> 00:20:47,160
You could down a whole tray in one go.

611
00:20:48,019 --> 00:20:49,539
Time really flies.

612
00:20:50,319 --> 00:20:51,519
So many years, just like that.

613
00:20:52,539 --> 00:20:53,519
This Forest Ranger job of yours,

614
00:20:54,400 --> 00:20:56,059
you've finally made something of it.

615
00:20:57,259 --> 00:20:58,900
With or without this armband,

616
00:20:59,319 --> 00:21:00,420
the job's the same.

617
00:21:00,460 --> 00:21:01,259
What else could I do?

618
00:21:02,559 --> 00:21:03,680
How have you been lately?

619
00:21:06,759 --> 00:21:07,480
I've been going on blind dates.

620
00:21:09,259 --> 00:21:10,319
I was thinking

621
00:21:10,839 --> 00:21:12,279
of finding someone in our village.

622
00:21:13,500 --> 00:21:14,400
Find someone

623
00:21:15,640 --> 00:21:16,900
I grew up with,

624
00:21:17,599 --> 00:21:18,779
someone I know inside out,

625
00:21:20,460 --> 00:21:21,980
and make do living together.

626
00:21:23,160 --> 00:21:24,839
No, you can't just settle.

627
00:21:25,140 --> 00:21:26,819
Life is yours to live.

628
00:21:27,119 --> 00:21:28,960
Besides, if you really want to find someone,

629
00:21:29,319 --> 00:21:31,220
you gotta find one with, with...

630
00:21:32,900 --> 00:21:34,359
a foundation of love.

631
00:21:36,539 --> 00:21:37,119
Love?

632
00:21:38,980 --> 00:21:41,160
My daughter taught me that.

633
00:21:42,140 --> 00:21:42,920
But I think

634
00:21:42,920 --> 00:21:44,000
what she said makes sense.

635
00:21:52,599 --> 00:21:53,099
Keep it.

636
00:21:53,640 --> 00:21:54,880
Wipe your sweat.

637
00:21:58,400 --> 00:21:58,880
Now go on.

638
00:21:59,400 --> 00:21:59,880
Okay, okay.

639
00:22:00,319 --> 00:22:00,700
Okay.

640
00:22:10,039 --> 00:22:10,759
Love

641
00:22:12,240 --> 00:22:12,720
Xiaofang

642
00:22:13,220 --> 00:22:14,279
Aunt wants to ask you something

643
00:22:14,700 --> 00:22:16,079
What do you think of Xiaocang

644
00:22:16,220 --> 00:22:16,640
as a person?

645
00:22:17,880 --> 00:22:18,660
Shu Qingcang?

646
00:22:19,859 --> 00:22:20,460
He's alright, I guess

647
00:22:22,079 --> 00:22:22,599
Alright?

648
00:22:23,420 --> 00:22:24,099
That's great!

649
00:22:25,980 --> 00:22:26,859
Then you should

650
00:22:26,960 --> 00:22:28,299
give it a real shot with him

651
00:22:31,799 --> 00:22:32,980
Why would I date him?

652
00:22:35,900 --> 00:22:36,440
Tell me

653
00:22:37,359 --> 00:22:39,940
are you really that clueless

654
00:22:39,940 --> 00:22:41,079
or just playing dumb?

655
00:22:41,640 --> 00:22:42,099
Look

656
00:22:42,680 --> 00:22:43,500
these past few days

657
00:22:43,859 --> 00:22:45,839
Xiaocang has done so much for our family

658
00:22:46,740 --> 00:22:48,359
First he dealt with the Qi family

659
00:22:48,599 --> 00:22:50,180
and let out our Yang family's frustration.

660
00:22:50,660 --> 00:22:51,559
Was that not just a misunderstanding?

661
00:22:53,259 --> 00:22:54,240
And your dad's job

662
00:22:55,019 --> 00:22:56,039
the job your dad has been dreaming of

663
00:22:56,039 --> 00:22:57,160
for all these years

664
00:22:57,420 --> 00:22:58,119
it finally came through, didn't it?

665
00:22:59,740 --> 00:23:01,640
Xiaocang has a real, steady job

666
00:23:01,900 --> 00:23:03,519
and he goes up the mountain with you every day

667
00:23:03,599 --> 00:23:04,339
to dig herbs

668
00:23:04,640 --> 00:23:06,240
He's clearly taken a liking to you

669
00:23:08,019 --> 00:23:09,480
This Xiaocang, you know

670
00:23:09,700 --> 00:23:12,160
He handles everything, inside and out

671
00:23:12,380 --> 00:23:13,259
He puts in real effort

672
00:23:13,380 --> 00:23:14,180
and he's sincere

673
00:23:15,299 --> 00:23:15,819
Xiaofang

674
00:23:16,140 --> 00:23:17,599
A plump duck like this

675
00:23:17,599 --> 00:23:18,380
right at your lips

676
00:23:19,119 --> 00:23:20,319
don't let it fly away!

677
00:23:21,339 --> 00:23:22,740
But I don't like him

678
00:23:23,339 --> 00:23:23,859
And besides

679
00:23:24,220 --> 00:23:25,960
there are no real feelings between us

680
00:23:26,519 --> 00:23:27,740
How could that ever lead to happiness?

681
00:23:29,339 --> 00:23:30,480
Look at all those novels and dramas

682
00:23:30,619 --> 00:23:31,579
Since ancient times

683
00:23:31,880 --> 00:23:33,480
plenty of couples got married first

684
00:23:33,519 --> 00:23:34,240
and fell in love later

685
00:23:35,000 --> 00:23:35,720
And another thing

686
00:23:36,119 --> 00:23:37,279
if he really marries you

687
00:23:37,740 --> 00:23:38,960
for the sake of his own future

688
00:23:39,440 --> 00:23:40,440
he'll have to treat you well

689
00:23:41,799 --> 00:23:42,839
What does any of that matter?

690
00:23:47,460 --> 00:23:48,720
Let me be straight with you

691
00:23:53,039 --> 00:23:54,000
Your Granduncle

692
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:55,720
wants a great-grandson

693
00:23:57,400 --> 00:23:58,759
He wants the one in your belly

694
00:23:59,059 --> 00:23:59,920
Yang Bite

695
00:24:10,200 --> 00:24:10,839
Xiaofang

696
00:24:12,039 --> 00:24:14,319
You'll always be Yang Bite's mom.

697
00:24:14,779 --> 00:24:16,339
That's a fact nothing can change.

698
00:24:17,200 --> 00:24:18,640
But have you thought about it?

699
00:24:18,900 --> 00:24:20,539
You have to work and earn money.

700
00:24:20,700 --> 00:24:21,579
Where would you find the time

701
00:24:21,579 --> 00:24:22,420
to take care of this child?

702
00:24:22,940 --> 00:24:23,420
Besides,

703
00:24:23,579 --> 00:24:24,819
you make so little money.

704
00:24:25,500 --> 00:24:26,460
What kind of living conditions

705
00:24:26,460 --> 00:24:27,740
could you give the child?

706
00:24:28,079 --> 00:24:30,180
If you give Yang Bite

707
00:24:30,339 --> 00:24:31,740
in Lineage adoption to Granduncle,

708
00:24:32,099 --> 00:24:33,660
it'd be totally different.

709
00:24:35,519 --> 00:24:37,559
The resources Granduncle can offer,

710
00:24:37,880 --> 00:24:38,839
the living conditions,

711
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:40,359
and the level of education,

712
00:24:40,779 --> 00:24:42,220
compared to you raising him yourself,

713
00:24:42,500 --> 00:24:44,519
it's a world of difference!

714
00:24:45,720 --> 00:24:46,960
You have to put yourself

715
00:24:47,000 --> 00:24:48,079
in the child's shoes

716
00:24:48,119 --> 00:24:49,279
and think about what's best for him.

717
00:24:49,819 --> 00:24:50,880
And think about your own future

718
00:24:50,880 --> 00:24:51,599
too.

719
00:24:52,960 --> 00:24:54,480
Assess the situation.

720
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:57,859
The wise adapt to the times.

721
00:24:58,500 --> 00:24:58,960
Got it?

722
00:24:59,920 --> 00:25:00,579
Aunt,

723
00:25:02,279 --> 00:25:04,099
giving my child away will make me happy?

724
00:25:05,460 --> 00:25:06,859
Is this the future you're talking about?

725
00:25:08,500 --> 00:25:11,160
Just listen to Aunt this once.

726
00:25:12,740 --> 00:25:13,680
My choice

727
00:25:14,299 --> 00:25:15,119
is the right one.

728
00:25:18,440 --> 00:25:19,140
I see it.

729
00:25:19,480 --> 00:25:20,339
I see it.

730
00:25:21,319 --> 00:25:22,920
Right here, right here.

731
00:25:24,240 --> 00:25:25,160
Here, Xiaofang, have some juice.

732
00:25:25,859 --> 00:25:27,359
Thanks, you're so attentive.

733
00:25:27,519 --> 00:25:28,180
Xiaofang,

734
00:25:28,940 --> 00:25:31,319
you're truly Granduncle's lucky star.

735
00:25:32,359 --> 00:25:33,799
Granduncle, you're too kind.

736
00:25:34,140 --> 00:25:36,079
You came to our family and did so much,

737
00:25:36,279 --> 00:25:37,579
put in so much effort.

738
00:25:37,940 --> 00:25:38,720
I'm very grateful.

739
00:25:38,980 --> 00:25:39,539
So

740
00:25:40,140 --> 00:25:41,420
I don't want you to lose out either.

741
00:25:41,779 --> 00:25:42,660
Of course.

742
00:25:43,279 --> 00:25:45,339
This is all what Granduncle should do.

743
00:25:46,940 --> 00:25:47,480
Granduncle,

744
00:25:47,900 --> 00:25:49,440
you want a great-grandson, right?

745
00:25:49,619 --> 00:25:50,980
Goes without saying.

746
00:25:52,940 --> 00:25:53,640
But are you sure

747
00:25:53,640 --> 00:25:56,240
what I'm carrying is a boy?

748
00:25:57,000 --> 00:25:57,799
Well, this...

749
00:25:58,920 --> 00:26:00,759
The ultrasound clearly shows a boy.

750
00:26:02,380 --> 00:26:03,140
The little guy,

751
00:26:03,700 --> 00:26:05,200
this is a little boy, right?

752
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:06,559
Yes, yes, yes.

753
00:26:07,180 --> 00:26:08,000
This is our

754
00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:09,319
Yang family's bloodline!

755
00:26:10,279 --> 00:26:11,400
But Granduncle, look,

756
00:26:14,000 --> 00:26:16,180
what's this?

757
00:26:16,519 --> 00:26:18,660
The little boy turned into a finger!

758
00:26:22,160 --> 00:26:22,759
Granduncle

759
00:26:23,299 --> 00:26:25,119
Let's play a Mystery box game.

760
00:26:25,880 --> 00:26:26,619
Mystery box?

761
00:26:26,880 --> 00:26:27,440
That's right.

762
00:26:27,759 --> 00:26:29,599
My belly is a Mystery box.

763
00:26:29,680 --> 00:26:30,619
Let's make a bet.

764
00:26:30,839 --> 00:26:31,940
Is it a boy inside,

765
00:26:31,940 --> 00:26:32,839
or a girl?

766
00:26:33,099 --> 00:26:34,940
But opening a Mystery box costs money.

767
00:26:35,140 --> 00:26:35,619
Not much.

768
00:26:36,220 --> 00:26:38,440
With a belly this big,

769
00:26:39,420 --> 00:26:40,279
let's just say one million.

770
00:26:40,500 --> 00:26:41,359
And once it's born,

771
00:26:41,359 --> 00:26:42,319
whether boy or girl,

772
00:26:42,559 --> 00:26:43,440
no returns or exchanges.

773
00:26:43,460 --> 00:26:44,140
Uncle Yang, Uncle Yang!

774
00:26:44,759 --> 00:26:45,519
Xiaofang, how can you talk

775
00:26:45,519 --> 00:26:46,579
to Granduncle like that?

776
00:26:47,160 --> 00:26:48,039
What did I do?

777
00:26:48,039 --> 00:26:49,440
Granduncle's been so good to me.

778
00:26:49,559 --> 00:26:50,960
Would I let him get shortchanged?

779
00:26:51,180 --> 00:26:51,680
Granduncle,

780
00:26:51,859 --> 00:26:52,799
we're doing business here.

781
00:26:52,799 --> 00:26:54,160
I've got to get the money I'm owed

782
00:26:54,160 --> 00:26:54,880
upfront.

783
00:26:55,440 --> 00:26:56,960
Wait, you, this...

784
00:26:57,920 --> 00:26:58,980
Oh right, Shu Qingcang.

785
00:27:02,640 --> 00:27:03,839
I'll agree to be Mrs. Shu.

786
00:27:04,339 --> 00:27:05,480
Don't you like me?

787
00:27:05,799 --> 00:27:07,019
Let's go get married right now.

788
00:27:07,579 --> 00:27:09,400
What if I give birth to a girl

789
00:27:10,380 --> 00:27:11,079
and Granduncle doesn't want it?

790
00:27:11,720 --> 00:27:12,720
Then you'd back out too,

791
00:27:13,259 --> 00:27:14,079
and I'd miss out on

792
00:27:14,079 --> 00:27:15,019
such a great husband.

793
00:27:18,779 --> 00:27:19,759
Aw, you're shy.

794
00:27:20,319 --> 00:27:21,619
I'll grab my ID and wait for you.

795
00:27:23,660 --> 00:27:24,339
Granduncle,

796
00:27:24,660 --> 00:27:25,700
I'll come see you next time.

797
00:27:27,559 --> 00:27:28,339
Wait, Xiaofang, you...

798
00:27:30,779 --> 00:27:31,279
Xiao Shu!

799
00:27:32,220 --> 00:27:33,240
Get my heart pills!

800
00:27:33,740 --> 00:27:34,440
I've got them, I've got them.

801
00:27:34,980 --> 00:27:36,339
Here, here, take these.

802
00:27:37,480 --> 00:27:38,220
Easy, easy, easy.

803
00:27:38,880 --> 00:27:39,819
Okay, easy, easy, easy.

804
00:27:40,359 --> 00:27:40,900
Easy now.

805
00:27:41,700 --> 00:27:42,380
Unbelievable.

806
00:27:46,220 --> 00:27:47,980
Still in the womb and already this fierce.

807
00:27:48,680 --> 00:27:49,380
Once it's born,

808
00:27:49,519 --> 00:27:50,440
it'll be just like its mother,

809
00:27:50,480 --> 00:27:51,359
turning the world upside down!

810
00:27:51,640 --> 00:27:53,579
A girl's fine, a girl's great!

811
00:27:54,559 --> 00:27:55,799
What's so great about it?

812
00:27:56,380 --> 00:27:57,759
You're just raising her for someone else.

813
00:27:58,680 --> 00:28:00,140
Your brain's really pickled in soy sauce.

814
00:28:00,880 --> 00:28:01,519
Look at nowadays,

815
00:28:01,859 --> 00:28:02,980
how much you get for marrying off a daughter.

816
00:28:03,579 --> 00:28:04,900
Sons are the money-losers now.

817
00:28:05,500 --> 00:28:06,319
Favoring boys over girls?

818
00:28:06,319 --> 00:28:07,799
That's ancient history.

819
00:28:09,359 --> 00:28:09,940
Girls are great.

820
00:28:10,960 --> 00:28:12,720
You can collect a fortune down the line.

821
00:28:18,599 --> 00:28:19,480
You're obsessed with money.

822
00:28:21,119 --> 00:28:23,059
Two heads!

823
00:28:25,000 --> 00:28:26,380
When my granddaughter marries,

824
00:28:26,380 --> 00:28:27,720
that's another fortune.

825
00:28:30,380 --> 00:28:31,119
Such a great deal!

826
00:28:32,359 --> 00:28:33,220
What are you muttering about?

827
00:28:34,420 --> 00:28:35,319
I, I was just saying...

828
00:28:35,700 --> 00:28:36,740
You gave me two sons,

829
00:28:37,039 --> 00:28:38,200
and I finally get a granddaughter.

830
00:28:38,200 --> 00:28:38,859
I'm happy!

831
00:28:40,200 --> 00:28:40,859
Where's your son?

832
00:28:41,660 --> 00:28:42,460
Lying upstairs.

833
00:28:43,259 --> 00:28:44,259
Useless piece of work.

834
00:28:46,539 --> 00:28:47,420
What's this?

835
00:28:48,740 --> 00:28:49,400
A finger.

836
00:28:50,859 --> 00:28:51,799
And what's this?

837
00:28:53,279 --> 00:28:53,779
A great-grandson.

838
00:28:54,519 --> 00:28:55,720
Definitely a great-grandson.

839
00:28:59,380 --> 00:29:01,559
That Yang Xiaofang is just fooling me.

840
00:29:01,599 --> 00:29:02,339
Yes, yes, yes.

841
00:29:02,839 --> 00:29:04,900
She just doesn't want me to have a great-grandson.

842
00:29:05,140 --> 00:29:05,559
Right.

843
00:29:08,819 --> 00:29:09,779
Didn't you say

844
00:29:10,880 --> 00:29:12,579
Yang Xiaofang agreed to marry you?

845
00:29:13,839 --> 00:29:15,319
You even guaranteed it to me.

846
00:29:15,960 --> 00:29:17,559
You want a future? I'll get it for you.

847
00:29:17,799 --> 00:29:19,039
But where's my great-grandson?

848
00:29:19,940 --> 00:29:20,420
Great-grandson?

849
00:29:21,099 --> 00:29:22,119
You'll definitely have a great-grandson.

850
00:29:22,539 --> 00:29:23,180
Guaranteed.

851
00:29:23,339 --> 00:29:23,960
Guaranteed, guaranteed.

852
00:29:26,059 --> 00:29:27,640
Just give me a little more time.

853
00:29:28,019 --> 00:29:29,599
I'll definitely get Yang Xiaofang to marry me.

854
00:29:30,240 --> 00:29:30,880
And by then,

855
00:29:31,119 --> 00:29:32,519
you'll be the great-grandson in her belly—

856
00:29:35,960 --> 00:29:37,359
the... the child in her belly

857
00:29:37,400 --> 00:29:38,359
will be your great-grandson.

858
00:29:54,859 --> 00:29:55,799
It's out! It's out!

859
00:29:58,440 --> 00:29:59,619
Uncle Yang, this is a good omen!

860
00:30:00,240 --> 00:30:00,819
A great-grandson.

861
00:30:01,519 --> 00:30:02,660
You're definitely getting a great-grandson.

862
00:30:12,599 --> 00:30:12,920
Grandma.

863
00:30:13,279 --> 00:30:14,480
I'll hang this mosquito-repelling

864
00:30:14,480 --> 00:30:15,180
herb pouch on you.

865
00:30:15,380 --> 00:30:16,240
Then you won't get bitten.

866
00:30:16,759 --> 00:30:17,319
Smells nice, right?

867
00:30:19,039 --> 00:30:19,500
Yes, it does.

868
00:30:23,079 --> 00:30:25,279
Did you really do that

869
00:30:25,859 --> 00:30:26,700
right in front of them?

870
00:30:27,420 --> 00:30:28,200
Of course.

871
00:30:28,279 --> 00:30:29,339
Right in their faces,

872
00:30:29,359 --> 00:30:30,339
just... like this.

873
00:30:30,980 --> 00:30:32,099
Who's gonna spoil them?

874
00:30:33,579 --> 00:30:35,460
You're full of sneaky tricks.

875
00:30:36,400 --> 00:30:38,839
Actually, boy or girl, it's all good.

876
00:30:39,279 --> 00:30:41,519
It's a blessing from the heavens.

877
00:30:41,819 --> 00:30:42,980
We should welcome it either way.

878
00:30:49,420 --> 00:30:50,640
Grandma, let me ask you quietly.

879
00:30:51,019 --> 00:30:52,259
We won't let Bite know.

880
00:30:52,779 --> 00:30:55,059
Do you prefer a great-grandson or granddaughter?

881
00:30:59,680 --> 00:31:01,519
I love them both, boy or girl.

882
00:31:02,779 --> 00:31:03,980
The stars up in the sky

883
00:31:04,400 --> 00:31:06,220
and the fireflies down on earth,

884
00:31:06,619 --> 00:31:08,019
which one isn't precious?

885
00:31:13,019 --> 00:31:14,319
Bite.

886
00:31:14,500 --> 00:31:15,299
Even inside the belly,

887
00:31:15,299 --> 00:31:17,019
someone already loves you this much.

888
00:31:17,700 --> 00:31:18,799
You're so lucky.

889
00:31:21,759 --> 00:31:23,039
And I'm so happy too.

890
00:31:32,940 --> 00:31:33,400
Xiaowei.

891
00:31:34,019 --> 00:31:35,539
Xiaowei, wake up.

892
00:31:36,079 --> 00:31:37,380
You've been like this since you were a kid.

893
00:31:41,480 --> 00:31:42,279
What are you doing?

894
00:31:42,599 --> 00:31:43,200
Xiaowei...

895
00:31:44,640 --> 00:31:45,920
Dad let you down.

896
00:31:47,200 --> 00:31:48,920
It's my fault for being stingy.

897
00:31:49,380 --> 00:31:49,920
Back then...

898
00:31:50,200 --> 00:31:51,559
If I had just gladly

899
00:31:52,119 --> 00:31:53,140
handed over the wedding money,

900
00:31:53,619 --> 00:31:55,180
you and Xiaofang would be so happy now.

901
00:31:55,400 --> 00:31:56,779
You've been drinking this early?

902
00:31:57,140 --> 00:31:58,799
Dad admits his mistakes and fixes them.

903
00:32:00,099 --> 00:32:00,839
From now on,

904
00:32:01,099 --> 00:32:02,279
I support you in pursuing love.

905
00:32:02,859 --> 00:32:04,000
Don't be afraid of that Shu guy.

906
00:32:04,500 --> 00:32:05,960
In the face of my son's love,

907
00:32:06,099 --> 00:32:06,900
what is money?

908
00:32:07,259 --> 00:32:08,000
Son, come here.

909
00:32:08,299 --> 00:32:09,359
Let's spruce up today.

910
00:32:09,519 --> 00:32:09,920
Be good.

911
00:32:10,279 --> 00:32:11,000
Let's look sharp today.

912
00:32:11,279 --> 00:32:12,000
Get all dressed up nicely.

913
00:32:12,319 --> 00:32:12,599
Come on, come on.

914
00:32:12,599 --> 00:32:13,799
What are you doing, Dad?

915
00:32:14,900 --> 00:32:15,380
Wear this one.

916
00:32:17,440 --> 00:32:18,160
And this hairstyle...

917
00:32:18,779 --> 00:32:19,740
Let Dad fix it up for you.

918
00:32:20,720 --> 00:32:21,240
Dad knows.

919
00:32:21,579 --> 00:32:22,500
I'm very fashionable.

920
00:32:23,880 --> 00:32:24,380
Look.

921
00:32:25,200 --> 00:32:25,819
Absolutely stylish.

922
00:32:26,920 --> 00:32:27,259
See?

923
00:32:27,660 --> 00:32:28,339
Those gifts...

924
00:32:29,059 --> 00:32:29,720
Bring them along in a bit.

925
00:32:30,160 --> 00:32:30,839
We'll go to the Yang family's place.

926
00:32:31,839 --> 00:32:33,880
Today counts as our first

927
00:32:34,359 --> 00:32:34,880
formal visit.

928
00:32:35,279 --> 00:32:36,539
You must be on your best behavior.

929
00:32:36,880 --> 00:32:37,680
Remember that.

930
00:32:38,640 --> 00:32:39,140
Back then,

931
00:32:39,440 --> 00:32:40,980
how did you win Yang Xiaofang over?

932
00:32:41,160 --> 00:32:41,660
Today,

933
00:32:41,880 --> 00:32:43,079
you're gonna win her back for me.

934
00:32:43,779 --> 00:32:45,240
People need a bit of love in their lives.

935
00:32:45,619 --> 00:32:46,059
Dad understands.

936
00:32:46,420 --> 00:32:46,980
Love.

937
00:32:47,160 --> 00:32:47,980
I love you.

938
00:32:48,519 --> 00:32:49,220
Love.

939
00:32:52,380 --> 00:32:53,460
So this is the pig you got

940
00:32:53,460 --> 00:32:54,380
using that pig card?

941
00:32:55,359 --> 00:32:55,859
That's right.

942
00:32:56,059 --> 00:32:58,000
This pig looks so sturdy.

943
00:32:58,059 --> 00:32:59,420
It must taste delicious.

944
00:32:59,920 --> 00:33:00,920
You'd better stay away from it.

945
00:33:01,539 --> 00:33:03,119
This pig charges without holding back.

946
00:33:03,859 --> 00:33:05,359
The pig is here,

947
00:33:06,240 --> 00:33:07,019
but this pig...

948
00:33:09,460 --> 00:33:10,339
who's gonna slaughter it, Sis?

949
00:33:11,339 --> 00:33:12,140
What do you mean?

950
00:33:12,740 --> 00:33:14,019
I'm this pretty.

951
00:33:14,359 --> 00:33:15,079
Me, slaughter a pig?

952
00:33:16,119 --> 00:33:18,039
Only my brother can do this.

953
00:33:18,119 --> 00:33:18,440
Right.

954
00:33:19,000 --> 00:33:19,700
As for my dad,

955
00:33:20,079 --> 00:33:21,240
he went up the mountain this morning.

956
00:33:21,240 --> 00:33:22,599
He said the Forest Rangers have training today.

957
00:33:24,859 --> 00:33:25,700
Then who's gonna do it?

958
00:33:30,240 --> 00:33:31,039
Don't look at me.

959
00:33:31,039 --> 00:33:31,960
With my little frame,

960
00:33:32,259 --> 00:33:33,279
this pig could kill me.

961
00:33:33,539 --> 00:33:34,160
It's gotta be big sis then.

962
00:33:34,160 --> 00:33:34,880
Take the lead now.

963
00:33:34,880 --> 00:33:35,759
Why are you looking at me?

964
00:33:35,759 --> 00:33:36,819
Aren't you ashamed?

965
00:33:37,319 --> 00:33:37,940
You're the only

966
00:33:37,940 --> 00:33:38,819
guy here.

967
00:33:41,859 --> 00:33:42,759
You can call me little sister.

968
00:33:44,039 --> 00:33:44,420
Little sister.

969
00:33:44,960 --> 00:33:45,400
Little sister.

970
00:33:45,980 --> 00:33:46,619
I'm going to the bathroom.

971
00:33:49,980 --> 00:33:51,160
I'm off to do yoga.

972
00:33:51,720 --> 00:33:53,039
You, you, go easy!

973
00:33:53,259 --> 00:33:54,319
It stinks so bad.

974
00:33:54,599 --> 00:33:55,319
No way, no way.

975
00:33:56,420 --> 00:33:57,599
Little sisters, they all ran off.

976
00:34:04,960 --> 00:34:05,619
What the heck?

977
00:34:09,619 --> 00:34:10,440
Why is it you?

978
00:34:10,960 --> 00:34:11,900
Why can't it be me?

979
00:34:14,139 --> 00:34:15,159
It's you, of all people,

980
00:34:15,739 --> 00:34:16,639
out here taking out the trash?

981
00:34:18,420 --> 00:34:19,619
Let me broaden your horizons.

982
00:34:27,480 --> 00:34:28,300
Why are you running?

983
00:34:28,760 --> 00:34:29,739
Move, move, move!

984
00:34:29,840 --> 00:34:30,579
Get out of the way!

985
00:34:30,960 --> 00:34:31,780
A good dog doesn't block the road.

986
00:34:31,900 --> 00:34:32,760
Well, I am the dog.

987
00:34:36,239 --> 00:34:37,260
You little punk, step aside!

988
00:34:37,340 --> 00:34:38,380
Aunt! Aunt!

989
00:34:38,639 --> 00:34:39,079
Xiaofang!

990
00:34:39,199 --> 00:34:39,539
Aunt!

991
00:34:39,539 --> 00:34:39,880
Coming!

992
00:34:39,960 --> 00:34:40,300
Aunt!

993
00:34:41,260 --> 00:34:42,119
Aunt! Aunt!

994
00:34:42,460 --> 00:34:42,960
Aunt!

995
00:34:43,739 --> 00:34:44,300
Xiaocang.

996
00:34:44,579 --> 00:34:46,480
Fresh plums, just washed for you.

997
00:34:46,480 --> 00:34:47,179
Thank you, Aunt.

998
00:34:47,179 --> 00:34:47,519
Come.

999
00:34:47,820 --> 00:34:48,420
Come, come, come.

1000
00:34:49,599 --> 00:34:50,280
Xiaocang's here.

1001
00:34:52,500 --> 00:34:53,679
He's a guest I invited.

1002
00:34:53,719 --> 00:34:54,099
Lately,

1003
00:34:54,099 --> 00:34:55,300
he's helped our family a lot.

1004
00:34:55,300 --> 00:34:55,679
Qingcang, Qingcang.

1005
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:57,659
Aunt, if there's any work to do,

1006
00:34:57,679 --> 00:34:58,219
I can help.

1007
00:35:00,420 --> 00:35:01,619
Aunt, I came to work too.

1008
00:35:01,639 --> 00:35:02,760
I can do any kind of work.

1009
00:35:02,800 --> 00:35:03,539
No need, no need.

1010
00:35:03,539 --> 00:35:04,920
You work at a desk, just take a rest.

1011
00:35:04,980 --> 00:35:05,619
What work could you possibly do?

1012
00:35:05,619 --> 00:35:06,300
Don't make me laugh.

1013
00:35:06,380 --> 00:35:07,420
After I get tired at the office,

1014
00:35:07,420 --> 00:35:08,760
I do manual work to relieve stress.

1015
00:35:10,659 --> 00:35:11,380
You're a guest.

1016
00:35:11,559 --> 00:35:12,179
Just rest well.

1017
00:35:12,179 --> 00:35:13,219
You're an artist.

1018
00:35:13,219 --> 00:35:14,019
Your hands can't get dirty.

1019
00:35:14,019 --> 00:35:14,380
No, wait.

1020
00:35:14,420 --> 00:35:15,460
How can a guest do work?

1021
00:35:15,480 --> 00:35:16,440
Stop fighting over it.

1022
00:35:16,860 --> 00:35:17,559
Today everyone's got work to do.

1023
00:35:17,880 --> 00:35:18,440
What is it?

1024
00:35:19,340 --> 00:35:19,840
Slaughtering a pig.

1025
00:35:27,900 --> 00:35:28,219
Okay.

1026
00:35:31,619 --> 00:35:32,139
What's wrong?

1027
00:35:33,679 --> 00:35:35,420
This pig is so pitiful.

1028
00:35:35,960 --> 00:35:37,539
So young and already getting slaughtered.

1029
00:35:38,900 --> 00:35:39,760
Can't help it.

1030
00:35:39,800 --> 00:35:40,820
It was born a pig.

1031
00:35:41,179 --> 00:35:42,659
Hope its next life is better.

1032
00:35:43,300 --> 00:35:44,480
Then let's go easy on it.

1033
00:35:44,659 --> 00:35:45,340
How's it going?

1034
00:35:47,260 --> 00:35:48,219
Can you handle it?

1035
00:35:48,639 --> 00:35:49,239
Come on!

1036
00:35:49,920 --> 00:35:51,219
When the tide goes out,

1037
00:35:52,079 --> 00:35:53,900
that's when you see who's sincere.

1038
00:35:54,539 --> 00:35:56,039
Since Xiaofang stopped going on blind dates,

1039
00:35:56,659 --> 00:35:57,599
no one comes around anymore.

1040
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:58,739
Only those two

1041
00:35:59,079 --> 00:36:00,139
still come by often.

1042
00:36:01,260 --> 00:36:02,619
Look at those two.

1043
00:36:02,880 --> 00:36:04,980
Clearly neither of them knows how to slaughter a pig.

1044
00:36:05,480 --> 00:36:06,599
But for Xiaofang's sake,

1045
00:36:07,219 --> 00:36:08,179
they're going all out to impress.

1046
00:36:08,619 --> 00:36:10,440
Those in the know say Xiaofang's picking.

1047
00:36:10,920 --> 00:36:11,880
Those who don't know,

1048
00:36:12,440 --> 00:36:13,239
they're saying out there

1049
00:36:13,480 --> 00:36:15,059
that Xiaofang's stringing along two men,

1050
00:36:15,440 --> 00:36:17,039
comparing their offers.

1051
00:36:17,800 --> 00:36:18,900
How about we vote?

1052
00:36:19,300 --> 00:36:20,320
Make the choice for Xiaofang.

1053
00:36:21,420 --> 00:36:22,119
Big sister, you go first.

1054
00:36:23,380 --> 00:36:24,500
Isn't it obvious?

1055
00:36:25,059 --> 00:36:25,659
Shu Qingcang.

1056
00:36:25,860 --> 00:36:26,719
Who invited him over?

1057
00:36:27,179 --> 00:36:27,780
Shu Qingcang.

1058
00:36:28,579 --> 00:36:29,260
He's educated.

1059
00:36:40,860 --> 00:36:41,840
Jingjing, you're here.

1060
00:36:43,139 --> 00:36:44,159
Come to my room for a minute.

1061
00:36:44,360 --> 00:36:45,360
I need to talk to you.

1062
00:36:52,039 --> 00:36:52,500
Jingjing.

1063
00:36:53,119 --> 00:36:53,579
Come, come, come.

1064
00:36:54,599 --> 00:36:54,880
Here.

1065
00:36:57,539 --> 00:36:58,280
Take a look.

1066
00:37:01,340 --> 00:37:02,119
Let me show you someone.

1067
00:37:02,739 --> 00:37:03,599
What do you think of him?

1068
00:37:04,559 --> 00:37:05,039
Have some water.

1069
00:37:06,579 --> 00:37:07,340
Careful.

1070
00:37:08,340 --> 00:37:09,219
What do you mean?

1071
00:37:10,260 --> 00:37:11,900
Young Shu, Shu Qingcang.

1072
00:37:12,360 --> 00:37:13,420
What do you think of him as a person?

1073
00:37:13,960 --> 00:37:14,679
What are you getting at?

1074
00:37:15,460 --> 00:37:17,039
Isn't he chasing after Xiaofang?

1075
00:37:18,619 --> 00:37:20,000
If Xiaofang doesn't fancy him,

1076
00:37:20,139 --> 00:37:21,239
those two won't work out anyway.

1077
00:37:22,159 --> 00:37:22,739
So I was thinking,

1078
00:37:23,099 --> 00:37:24,260
if you took a liking to him,

1079
00:37:24,659 --> 00:37:25,300
I could introduce

1080
00:37:25,300 --> 00:37:26,219
the two of you.

1081
00:37:29,139 --> 00:37:30,099
Unbelievable.

1082
00:37:30,320 --> 00:37:31,199
What's wrong with you?

1083
00:37:31,639 --> 00:37:33,400
You've gone too far, Yang Fanyan.

1084
00:37:33,639 --> 00:37:34,519
I rushed back here

1085
00:37:34,559 --> 00:37:35,780
thinking you'd finally agreed

1086
00:37:35,780 --> 00:37:36,360
to lend me the money.

1087
00:37:36,519 --> 00:37:37,059
But no.

1088
00:37:37,460 --> 00:37:38,519
You won't help me raise the money,

1089
00:37:38,880 --> 00:37:39,579
and you've still got time

1090
00:37:39,579 --> 00:37:40,699
to set me up with a man?

1091
00:37:40,980 --> 00:37:41,920
I don't have a mother like you.

1092
00:37:42,440 --> 00:37:43,480
This is beyond ridiculous.

1093
00:37:52,699 --> 00:37:53,840
Fighting with Aunt again?

1094
00:37:54,840 --> 00:37:55,280
Jingjing.

1095
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:56,340
Jingjing.

1096
00:38:01,400 --> 00:38:02,300
Still angry?

1097
00:38:10,420 --> 00:38:11,460
Don't be mad.

1098
00:38:13,179 --> 00:38:14,099
Look at you.

1099
00:38:14,860 --> 00:38:16,260
Got something good and didn't include me?

1100
00:38:17,440 --> 00:38:18,760
Trying to keep it all to yourself again?

1101
00:38:20,079 --> 00:38:21,460
What good thing?

1102
00:38:23,760 --> 00:38:24,199
Play dumb.

1103
00:38:25,260 --> 00:38:26,239
Keep playing dumb.

1104
00:38:30,380 --> 00:38:31,119
Come on now.

1105
00:38:31,760 --> 00:38:33,380
Don't just think about your own daughter.

1106
00:38:34,579 --> 00:38:35,219
Look,

1107
00:38:35,440 --> 00:38:37,260
if Xiaofang doesn't want Xiaocang,

1108
00:38:37,639 --> 00:38:38,639
and Jingjing doesn't either,

1109
00:38:39,579 --> 00:38:40,440
you've still got me, right?

1110
00:38:41,039 --> 00:38:41,719
I'm willing.

1111
00:38:44,599 --> 00:38:46,019
Have you no shame?

1112
00:38:46,920 --> 00:38:48,239
How old are you already?

1113
00:38:48,619 --> 00:38:49,800
Have you lost your mind?

1114
00:38:54,760 --> 00:38:56,300
Where's your head at?

1115
00:38:56,360 --> 00:38:57,719
What are you even thinking?

1116
00:38:59,659 --> 00:39:00,760
Last time at dinner,

1117
00:39:01,280 --> 00:39:02,820
Granduncle really adored Dandan, didn't he?

1118
00:39:03,679 --> 00:39:05,400
Granduncle wants a boy.

1119
00:39:06,000 --> 00:39:06,940
Isn't Dandan one?

1120
00:39:07,460 --> 00:39:08,360
I could give Dandan up

1121
00:39:08,820 --> 00:39:09,800
for Lineage adoption to Granduncle.

1122
00:39:11,800 --> 00:39:13,559
And you call yourself his mother!

1123
00:39:14,980 --> 00:39:15,739
Even if you're willing,

1124
00:39:16,079 --> 00:39:17,019
would Dandan be?

1125
00:39:18,039 --> 00:39:19,179
That kid doesn't know a damn thing.

1126
00:39:19,440 --> 00:39:20,260
I'm his mother.

1127
00:39:20,380 --> 00:39:21,280
I'm doing this for his own good.

1128
00:39:24,539 --> 00:39:25,480
As for Granduncle,

1129
00:39:25,840 --> 00:39:27,420
he just wants the title.

1130
00:39:28,159 --> 00:39:29,380
If Dandan goes through Lineage adoption,

1131
00:39:29,619 --> 00:39:30,760
it's just a formality.

1132
00:39:30,840 --> 00:39:31,400
Just change what he calls him.

1133
00:39:31,780 --> 00:39:33,380
He'd still stay with me, of course.

1134
00:39:33,719 --> 00:39:34,980
With Granduncle's means,

1135
00:39:35,300 --> 00:39:37,059
Dandan's schooling, his exams,

1136
00:39:37,480 --> 00:39:39,059
and getting into college,

1137
00:39:39,159 --> 00:39:40,079
we wouldn't have to worry about any of it.

1138
00:39:40,480 --> 00:39:41,800
Like his residency,

1139
00:39:42,179 --> 00:39:42,699
housing,

1140
00:39:43,519 --> 00:39:44,420
finding a wife later,

1141
00:39:44,579 --> 00:39:46,320
she'd definitely be a city girl.

1142
00:39:46,940 --> 00:39:48,420
You're really dreaming with your eyes open.

1143
00:39:49,820 --> 00:39:51,340
You're almost as bad as Qi Deyao across the way.

1144
00:39:51,599 --> 00:39:53,119
You're such a schemer!

1145
00:39:54,340 --> 00:39:55,039
This kind of thing,

1146
00:39:55,699 --> 00:39:56,420
it's not up to me.

1147
00:39:56,760 --> 00:39:58,980
Isn't Xiaocang here for exactly this?

1148
00:40:01,639 --> 00:40:02,940
Just ask him for me, sis.

1149
00:40:06,119 --> 00:40:07,659
Xiaocang, come here a sec.

1150
00:40:07,820 --> 00:40:09,719
Someone wants to ask you something.

1151
00:40:10,059 --> 00:40:11,820
Something very important.

1152
00:40:12,239 --> 00:40:13,079
Very important.

1153
00:40:13,079 --> 00:40:13,900
It's nothing, nothing.

1154
00:40:22,500 --> 00:40:24,059
What does Lineage adoption mean?

1155
00:40:25,699 --> 00:40:27,579
Lineage adoption is when you give your own son

1156
00:40:27,639 --> 00:40:28,960
to a brother who has no son

1157
00:40:29,019 --> 00:40:30,440
or to a relative as their son.

1158
00:40:35,920 --> 00:40:37,639
Pig bro, have a bite.

1159
00:40:38,280 --> 00:40:38,820
Pig bro.

1160
00:40:39,360 --> 00:40:40,099
What VIP treatment.

1161
00:40:40,320 --> 00:40:40,619
Right?

1162
00:40:40,619 --> 00:40:42,219
Only gets this before slaughter.

1163
00:40:42,440 --> 00:40:43,179
Exactly.

1164
00:40:43,880 --> 00:40:44,340
Let's do it.

1165
00:40:49,460 --> 00:40:50,739
Sorry, buddy. Three, two, one.

1166
00:40:51,219 --> 00:40:53,280
Come on. Three, two, one.

1167
00:40:54,579 --> 00:40:56,139
Do you think, while it's asleep,

1168
00:40:56,420 --> 00:40:58,179
a stab would still hurt a lot?

1169
00:40:59,099 --> 00:41:00,460
Of course it'd hurt.

1170
00:41:01,619 --> 00:41:02,719
Nice, listening to music.

1171
00:41:07,820 --> 00:41:08,480
Xiaofang.

1172
00:41:08,860 --> 00:41:09,500
Is there any

1173
00:41:09,500 --> 00:41:10,639
other option?

1174
00:41:11,780 --> 00:41:12,380
Wh-what?

1175
00:41:12,820 --> 00:41:13,400
I think

1176
00:41:13,679 --> 00:41:14,420
it's too skinny.

1177
00:41:14,639 --> 00:41:15,820
How about we raise it a bit longer?

1178
00:41:15,860 --> 00:41:16,679
You noticed too, right?

1179
00:41:17,199 --> 00:41:18,340
We should keep it till New Year at least.

1180
00:41:18,559 --> 00:41:19,460
As a New Year pig. How's that?

1181
00:41:24,460 --> 00:41:24,820
Alright then.

1182
00:41:25,719 --> 00:41:27,179
Let's make a choice.

1183
00:41:27,659 --> 00:41:28,599
Decide its fate.

1184
00:41:29,559 --> 00:41:30,219
What do you choose?

1185
00:41:30,559 --> 00:41:31,280
I choose to set it free.

1186
00:41:31,300 --> 00:41:31,840
What do you choose?

1187
00:41:32,239 --> 00:41:33,460
I choose to let it

1188
00:41:33,760 --> 00:41:34,900
go into the forest.

1189
00:41:35,039 --> 00:41:36,099
Just think, in the big forest,

1190
00:41:36,099 --> 00:41:36,679
there's so much good food.

1191
00:41:36,679 --> 00:41:37,559
What big forest?

1192
00:41:37,559 --> 00:41:38,820
Send it to the creek.

1193
00:41:38,860 --> 00:41:39,900
What's at the creek?

1194
00:41:40,380 --> 00:41:41,260
The creek.

1195
00:41:41,519 --> 00:41:42,260
It'll suffer a bit now,

1196
00:41:42,260 --> 00:41:43,579
but it'll thank me later.

1197
00:41:43,679 --> 00:41:44,340
Thank you for what?

1198
00:41:44,340 --> 00:41:45,940
I'm a pig-slaughtering maniac. As if I don't know

1199
00:41:46,119 --> 00:41:48,679
where a piglet ends up eventually?

1200
00:41:48,820 --> 00:41:50,119
It'll definitely thank me in the future.

1201
00:41:50,179 --> 00:41:51,159
It's a pig. What does it know?

1202
00:41:56,039 --> 00:41:57,219
How about we vote?

1203
00:41:57,800 --> 00:41:59,039
Help Xiaofang make a choice.

1204
00:42:00,440 --> 00:42:01,980
Choose for it, for its own good.

1205
00:42:02,980 --> 00:42:04,460
Does a pig need your fake mercy?

1206
00:42:04,460 --> 00:42:05,639
It's a domestic pig.

1207
00:42:05,679 --> 00:42:06,900
Setting it free means death anyway.

1208
00:42:07,840 --> 00:42:08,659
Quit being dramatic.

1209
00:42:36,440 --> 00:42:37,300
Damn, that's fierce!

1210
00:42:54,900 --> 00:42:55,340
Grandma

1211
00:42:56,480 --> 00:42:57,699
About that choice everyone's talking about,

1212
00:42:57,699 --> 00:42:58,539
which would you pick?

1213
00:43:05,840 --> 00:43:06,800
I choose

1214
00:43:11,199 --> 00:43:12,239
to feast on meat.

1215
00:43:19,920 --> 00:43:20,719
So good!

1216
00:43:23,360 --> 00:43:24,760
Weren't they saying Dandan went missing?

1217
00:43:25,639 --> 00:43:26,440
How did Xiaofang and Jingjing

1218
00:43:26,460 --> 00:43:27,579
end up running away too?

1219
00:43:27,619 --> 00:43:29,059
Why did you take so long?

1220
00:43:29,639 --> 00:43:30,420
What's going on here?

1221
00:43:30,760 --> 00:43:31,860
I heard Xiaofang ran away.

1222
00:43:32,340 --> 00:43:33,059
We can't find her anywhere.

1223
00:43:33,420 --> 00:43:34,460
I want to report it.

1224
00:43:34,460 --> 00:43:36,099
Please send officers right away!

1225
00:43:36,360 --> 00:43:37,679
What if she's been trafficked?

1226
00:43:38,440 --> 00:43:39,460
Don't let him touch my leg!

1227
00:43:40,139 --> 00:43:40,840
Help!

1228
00:43:41,280 --> 00:43:42,079
If you want to make money,

1229
00:43:42,820 --> 00:43:44,199
don't treat yourself like a human,

1230
00:43:44,739 --> 00:43:46,000
and don't treat others like humans either.

1231
00:43:46,219 --> 00:43:47,099
Get up, get up, something happened!

1232
00:43:47,300 --> 00:43:48,659
Look at the time! Stop sleeping, get up!

1233
00:43:50,039 --> 00:43:50,820
He couldn't have

1234
00:43:50,900 --> 00:43:52,400
actually run off with Xiaofang, could he?

